    "title": "Job Opening Hotel Manager at Ananda in the Himalayas Ventures Solutions",
    "description": "If you're a passionate Hotel Manager with drive and ambition, Ananda in the Himalayas Ventures Solutions in Meerut is the place for you. We're growing fast and need talented people to grow with us.\n\nAbout Ananda in the Himalayas Ventures Solutions:\nAnanda in the Himalayas Ventures Solutions is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Monitor F&B service quality and maintain hygiene standards\n• Prepare daily operating reports and present to management\n• Handle guest complaints and resolve issues promptly\n• Assist in menu planning, costing, and food festival coordination\n• Manage reservations and optimize room revenue through yield management\n• Conduct regular guest satisfaction surveys and implement improvements\n• Ensure compliance with FSSAI, health, and safety regulations\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• B.Arch / M.Arch from recognized institution\n• 0-1 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Housekeeping Standards\n• Proficiency in HACCP\n• Proficiency in Travel Management\n• Proficiency in Hotel Management\n• Proficiency in Front Office\n• Proficiency in Yield Management\n• Proficiency in Crisis Management\n• Proficiency in OTA Management\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Professional development and training programs\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Annual performance appraisal\n• Company-sponsored certifications\n• Transportation and conveyance allowance\n• Meal coupons and food allowance\n• Salary Range: 2.5 LPA - 6 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Meerut, Uttar Pradesh, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Ananda in the Himalayas Ventures Solutions!",
